        "text": "In fact, ML is a a black box for most people, even for those AI experts! :sweat_smile:\n\nAnd, on the contrary, I find that bringing people to create their own image classification models with Teachable Machine and making them use it from adacraft (or any Scratch with AI extension, there are others) helps them figure out what ML means, and particularly in terms of bias. I have done it several times since one year during workshops and it is very demonstrative.",
